Metro Plans Online Shops for Saturn, Media Markt, Welt Reports

-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 
2011-07-17T12:47:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-17/metro-plans-online-shops-for-saturn-media-markt-welt-reports.html
Metro AG (MEO) ’s Saturn store chain plans
to start online sales in  Germany  in the fourth quarter,  Die Welt 
reported, citing Chief Executive Officer Eckhard Cordes.  The Media Markt unit will begin selling online in the first
half of 2012, Cordes also told the newspaper.  Internet sales  may contribute 30 percent of overall revenue
in “saturated markets” like Germany in the medium term, the
executive was cited as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Cornelius Rahn in Frankfurt at 
 crahn2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong in Berlin at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  